  ($gb$montroseterrace-babylonstoren$gb$, $gb$Babylonstoren$gb$, $gb$activities$gb$, $gb$<p>Babylonstoren is one of the oldest Cape Dutch farms, set at the foot of Simonsberg in the Franschhoek wine valley. There is lots to see and do on this working farm</p>$gb$, $gb$Babylonstoren, Klapmuts - Simondium Rd, Simondium, 7670, South Africa$gb$, $gb$+27 21 863 3852$gb$, $gb$https://www.babylonstoren.com/$gb$, $gb$https://storage.googleapis.com/hostfully-dev-filestack/i3SQgoWVT46uSsKD9KG9$gb$, -33.8239354, 18.92635),
