  ($gb$montroseterrace-high-tea-in-the-cape$gb$, $gb$High Tea in the Cape$gb$, $gb$Places to eat$gb$, $gb$<p><a href="https://www.belmond.com/hotels/africa/south-africa/cape-town/belmond-mount-nelson-hotel/" target="_blank" style="color: black;"><strong><u>Belmond Mount Nelson Hotel</u></strong></a></p><p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">(76 Orange Street, Gardens, Cape Town, 8001)</span></p><p>+27 21 483 1000 // <u style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);">r</u><a href="mailto:restaurantreservations.mnh@belmond.com" target="_blank" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);"><u>estaurantreservations.mnh</u></a><a href="mailto:restaurantreservations.mnh@belmond.com" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><u>@belmond.c</u></a><a href="mailto:restaurantreservations.mnh@belmond.com" target="_blank" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);"><u>om</u></a></p><p>Embrace tradition with an elegant afternoon tea. While you dine on sumptuous cakes, pastries and sandwiches stacked in tiers, live piano music sets the scene.</p><ul><li>Mondays - Sundays (9:30 a.m. - 11:30 a.m.) - Morning Tea</li><li>Mondays - Sundays (1:00 p.m. - 5:30 p.m.) - Afternoon Tea</li><li>Mondays - Sundays (6:00 p.m. - 8:30 p.m.) - Evening Tea</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><a href="https://www.12apostleshotel.com/food-and-drink/the-leopard-bar" target="_blank" style="color: black;"><strong><u>The Leopard Bar</u></strong></a></p><p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">(The 12 Apostles Hotel, Victoria Street, Camps Bay, 8005)</span></p><p>+27 21 437 9000 // <u>reservations1</u><a href="mailto:reservations1@12apostles.co.za" target="_blank" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u>@12apostles.c</u></a><u>o.za</u></p><p><span style="color: rgb(112, 112, 112);">Is a great spot to enjoy "Tea by the Sea", a delicious afternoon tea with all the trimmings, from chocolate brownies to scones and sandwiches.</span></p><ul><li>Mondays - Sundays (10:00 a.m. - 4:00 p.m.)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><a href="https://www.theroyalportfolio.com/the-silo/experiences/at/eating-drinking-at-the-silo-hotel/" target="_blank" style="color: black;"><strong>The Silo Hotel</strong></a></p><p><span style="color: black;">(Silo Square, V&A Waterfront, Cape Town, </span>8001)</p><p>+27 21 670 0500 // <a href="mailto:dining@thesilohotel.com" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">dining@thesilohotel.com</a></p><p><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">Enjoy a selection of sweet treats including the cake of the day as well as a variety of savoury snacks. Reservations must be made.</span></p><ul><li>Mondays - Sundays (2:00 p.m. - 5:00 p.m.)</li></ul>$gb$, $gb$Cape Town, South Africa$gb$, null, $gb$https://www.capetown.travel/the-10-best-places-for-high-tea-in-cape-town/$gb$, $gb$https://storage.googleapis.com/hostfully-dev-filestack/JWqjegBmSBiQkNK46TXp$gb$, -33.9248685, 18.424055299999964),
