  ($gb$montroseterrace-kirstenbosch-national-botanical-garden$gb$, $gb$Kirstenbosch National Botanical Garden$gb$, $gb$attractions$gb$, $gb$<p>Picnics are allowed in Kirstenbosch, but you are not permitted to take chairs, tables, umbrellas, tents, etc. into the Garden. Picnic hampers and/or takeaways are available from the Kirstenbosch Tea Room and Moyo Restaurant.</p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);">At Kirstenbosch you can:</span></p><ul><li>Discover plants and animals</li><li>Explore the Garden, the forest and the fynbos</li><li>Walk</li><li>Hike</li><li>Birdwatch</li><li>Take photographs</li><li>Picnic</li><li>Relax at concerts</li><li>Enjoy sculptures and art</li></ul><p><br /></p><h3><strong><u>Contact Details for Kirstenbosch Gardens:</u></strong></h3><p><br /></p><p>Tel: +27 21 799 8783</p><p>Email: <a href="mailto:Kirstenboschinfo@sanbi.org" target="_blank" style="color: black; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>Kirstenboschinfo@sanbi.org</strong></a></p><p>Address: <a href="https://www.google.co.za/maps/place/Kirstenbosch+National+Botanical+Garden/@-33.9875011,18.432722,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x1b7c8ad971eaa566!8m2!3d-33.9875011!4d18.432722" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">Rhodes Drive, Newlands, 7735</a></p><p>Hours:</p><ul><li>Mondays - Sundays (8:00 a.m. - 7:00 p.m.) - September to March</li><li>Mondays - Sundays (8:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m.) - April to August</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong><u>Cost</u></strong></p><p>(View website for entry fees.)</p>$gb$, $gb$Kirstenbosch National Botanical Garden, Rhodes Dr, Newlands, Cape Town, 7735, South Africa$gb$, $gb$+27 21 799 8783$gb$, $gb$http://www.sanbi.org/gardens/kirstenbosch$gb$, $gb$https://storage.googleapis.com/hostfully-dev-filestack/RBtqhEUORoOHWYdAZTIi$gb$, -33.9875011, 18.432722000000012),
