  ($gb$montroseterrace-shopping-malls$gb$, $gb$Shopping Malls$gb$, $gb$shopping$gb$, $gb$<p><a href="https://www.constantiavillage.co.za/" target="_blank" style="color: black;"><strong>Constantia Village Shopping Centre</strong></a></p><p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">(Constantia Main Road & Spaanschemat River Roads, 7806)</span></p><p>+27 21 794 5065</p><p><span style="color: black;">Nestled under trees and laid out with a village feel. If you’re looking for an outfit, gift or the perfect bouquet, you will find all of it amongst the variety of boutiques and upmarket gift stores. It is the biggest shopping centre in Constantia and has a Woolworths & Pick n Pay for food shopping, as well as Pharmacies, and a number of other retail stores. It gets very busy over the Christmas season, so get there early</span><strong style="color: black;">.  </strong></p><ul><li>Mondays - Fridays (9:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m)</li><li>Saturdays (9:00 a.m. - 5:00 p.m)</li><li>Sundays (9:00 a.m. - 2:00 p.m)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><a href="http://www.steenbergvillage.com/" target="_blank" style="color: black;"><strong>Steenberg Village</strong></a></p><p><strong>(</strong>Reddam Avenue, Tokai, 7945)</p><p>+27 419 7373</p><p><span style="color: black;">A smaller shopping centre, but has a Woolworths and Pick n Pay. There is also a gorgeous gift shop called "Sand", that has swimwear, gifts, and interior items. </span><a href="http://www.jakes.co.za/" target="_blank" style="color: black;"><strong>Jakes</strong></a><span style="color: black;"> is a popular restaurant frequented by locals in the area at this centre.</span></p><ul><li>Mondays - Fridays (8:30 a.m. - 6:00 p.m)</li><li>Saturdays & Sundays (9:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><a href="https://shopconstantiaemporium.com" target="_blank"><strong>Constantia Emporium</strong></a></p><p><strong>(</strong><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"> M39, Belle Constantia, Cape Town, 7806)</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">A new shopping centre, having just opened in November 2019, it has a large Checkers, grocery store and a Woolworths, plus a few other stores. Parking is easier at this centre.</span></p><p><br /></p><p><a href="http://www.cavendish.co.za/" target="_blank" style="color: black;"><strong>Cavendish Square</strong></a></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);">(Dreyer Street, Claremont, 7708)</span></p><p>+27 21 657 5600 // <a href="mailto:info@cavendish.co.za" target="_blank" style="color: black;">info@cavendish.co.za</a></p><p><span style="color: black;">All the larger stores will be found here, an H&M, and Office Fashion Footwear stores have recently opened at this centre.</span></p><ul><li>Mondays - Saturdays (9:00 a.m. - 7:00 p.m)</li><li>Sundays (10:00 a.m. - 5:00 p.m)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><a href="http://www.waterfront.co.za/" target="_blank" style="color: black;"><strong>V&A Waterfront</strong></a></p><p>(19 Dock Road, V&A Waterfront, Cape Town, 8001)</p><p>+27 21 408 7600 //<strong> </strong><a href="mailto:info@waterfront.co.za" target="_blank" style="color: black;">info@waterfront.co.za</a></p><p>One of Cape Town's biggest tourist attractions and South Africa's most visited destination. This busy commercial harbour is set in the midst of a great entertainment venue with restaurants, pubs, craft markets, gift shops, a Ferris Wheel, and theaters. I<span style="color: black;">t does get very touristy over peak season, though. The </span><a href="http://www.waterfront.co.za/Shop/watershed" target="_blank" style="color: black; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>Watershed</strong></a><u style="color: black;">,</u><span style="color: black;"> houses the best local art and design, and is a great place for picking up typically South African gifts.</span></p><ul><li>Mondays - Sundays (9:00 a.m. - 9:00 p.m)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><a href="https://canalwalk.co.za/" target="_blank" style="color: black;"><strong>Canal Walk</strong></a></p><p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">(Century </span><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);">Boulevard</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">, Century City, Cape Town, 7441)</span></p><p>+27 21 529 9699</p><p>With over 400 stores, Canal Walk is the largest shopping centre in Cape Town, and the 3rd largest in South Africa.</p><p><span style="color: rgb(84, 84, 84);">Ranging from fashion, footwear, home décor, jewellery, movies, health & beauty, books, entertainment, and many more.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(84, 84, 84);">Find a complete list here: </span><a href="https://canalwalk.co.za/shops" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(84, 84, 84);"><strong>Canal Walk All Shops</strong></a></p><ul><li>Mondays - Sundays (9:00 a.m. - 9:00 p.m)</li></ul>$gb$, $gb$Cape Town, South Africa$gb$, null, null, $gb$https://storage.googleapis.com/hostfully-dev-filestack/hqvqolVTSM1AlHF8CZvH$gb$, -33.9248685, 18.424055299999964),
