  ($gb$montroseterrace-the-silo-hotel$gb$, $gb$The Silo Hotel$gb$, $gb$attractions$gb$, $gb$<p>Surrounded by ocean and Cape Town's beautiful mountains, The Silo Hotel offers a wide range of features to enjoy:</p><ul><li>The Granary Café</li><li>The Willaston Bar</li><li>Sky Terrace</li><li>High Tea</li><li>Rooftop Bar and Restaurant</li><li>Rooftop Swimming Pool</li><li>Spa</li><li>Gym</li><li>Free WiFi</li><li>Secure Underground Parking</li></ul><p><br /></p><h3><strong><u>Contact Details for The Silo Hotel:</u></strong></h3><p><br /></p><p>Tel: +27 21 670 0500</p><p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@thesilohotel.com" target="_blank" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: black;"><strong>info@thesilohotel.</strong></a><strong style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: black;">com</strong></p><p>Address: <span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">Silo Square, V&A Waterfront, 8801</span></p><p>Hours:</p><ul><li>Mondays - Sundays (7:00 a.m. - 10:30 p.m.)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong><u>Cost</u></strong></p><p>Mondays - Sundays:</p><ul><li>Adults (R180.00)</li><li>Under 18's (Free)</li></ul>$gb$, $gb$Silo Square, V & A Waterfront, Cape Town, 8801, South Africa$gb$, $gb$+27 21 670 0500$gb$, $gb$http://www.theroyalportfolio.com/thesilo$gb$, $gb$https://storage.googleapis.com/hostfully-dev-filestack/z5dCZaWHSoq9lJ6WmdPQ$gb$, -33.90861, 18.422714000000042),
