  ($gb$montroseterrace-jarod-s-performance-training-personal-trainer$gb$, $gb$Jarod's Performance Training - Personal Trainer$gb$, $gb$Health & Wellness$gb$, $gb$<p style="padding-left: 0rem"><img width="144" class="inline-left" /><span style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12ptpx"><strong>✨</strong></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx"><strong> </strong></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14ptpx"><strong>JPT – Jarod’s Performance Training </strong></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14ptpx"><strong>✨</strong></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14ptpx"><br /><strong>On-Site Personal Training & Massage Therapy for Airbnb Guests</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx">Upgrade your stay with private, professional wellness services delivered straight to your villa.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong>💪</strong></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong> Personal Training (JPT – Jarod’s Performance Training)</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx">Custom sessions designed around <em>your goals</em>, available for:<br />• <strong>Individuals</strong><br />• <strong>Couples</strong><br />• <strong>Small groups (2–5 people)</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx">Training options include:<br />• Fat-burning & cardio-focused workouts<br />• Strength & conditioning<br />• Mobility & flexibility sessions<br />• Minimal-equipment or no-equipment training<br />• Beginner-friendly or advanced programs</span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx">Stay active, stay motivated, and make the most of your stay.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong>💆</strong></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong> Massage Therapy</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx">Relax, recover, and release tension with in-home massage.<br />Available styles:<br />• Swedish / Relaxation<br />• Deep Tissue<br />• Sports Massage<br />• Targeted pain relief (neck, back, shoulders, legs)</span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong>🕒</strong></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong> Flexible Scheduling</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx">Morning, afternoon, or evening—whenever works best for you.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong>📍</strong></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong> We Come to You</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx">All services provided directly in the comfort of your villa</span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong>📞</strong></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 13.5ptpx"><strong> Book Your Session</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx"><strong>WhatsApp / Cell: +27 64 521 6983</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12ptpx">Send a message to check availability, pricing, or build a custom wellness package.</span></p>$gb$, $gb$Cape Town, SA$gb$, $gb$+27 64 521 6983$gb$, null, $gb$https://gb-cdn.hostfully.com/production/04368486b18546f2ad809f774a46ca3f/Picture-1.png$gb$, 0, 0);

